column1: # Dot#        4-character identifier for a given station
# Ref_epoch   Date and time at which the station position is as given in ref_XYZ and ref_NEU. Format is YYYYMMDDhhmmss.
# Ref_X       Reference X coordinate at Ref_epoch
# Ref_Y       Reference Y coordinate at Ref_epoch
# Ref_Z       Reference Z coordinate at Ref_epoch
# Ref_Nlat    Reference North latitude WGS-84 ellipsoid
# Ref_Elong   Reference East Longitude WGS-84 ellipsoid
# dX/dt       X component of station velocity
# dY/dt       Y component of station velocity
# dZ/dt       Z component of station velocity
# SXd         Standard deviation of X velocity
# SYd         Standard deviation of Y velocity
# SZd         Standard deviation of Z velocity
# Rxy         Correlation of X and Y velocity
# Rxz         Correlation of X and Z velocity
# Ryz         Correlation of Y and Z velocity
# dN/dt       North component of station velocity
# dE/dt       East component of station velocity
# dU/dt       Vertical component of station velocity
# SNd         Standard deviation of North velocity
# SEd         Standard deviation of East velocity
# SUd         Standard deviation of vertical velocity
# Rne         Correlation of North and East velocity
# Rnu         Correlation of North and vertical velocity
# Reu         Correlation of East and vertical velocity
# first_epoch Epoch of first data used to derive the station velocity
column2: in the same format as ref_epoch.

column1: # last_epoch  Epoch of last data used to derive the station velocity
column2: in the same format as ref_epoch.
